</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-15"><a href="#Monitor_settings"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Monitor settings</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-16"><a href="#Manual_configuration"><span class="tocnumber">5.1</span> <span class="toctext">Manual configuration</span></a></li>
