<td><span class="plainlinks archwiki-template-pkg"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/lib32-nvidia-390xx-utils/">lib32-nvidia-390xx-utils</a></span><sup><small>AUR</small></sup>
